## 延伸阅读 Further Reading
　  

<p style="font:bold 150% sans-serif;">中华传统文化<br />
Chinese Traditional Culture</p>

<table style="width:100%;background-color:#efefef;border-collapse:collapse;">
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">1</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　中华传统文化是中华文明演化而汇集成的一种反映民族特质和风貌的民族文化，是民族历史上各种思想文化、观念形态的总体表征，是指居住在中国地域内的中华民族及其祖先所创造的、为中华民族世世代代所继承发展的、具有鲜明民族特色的、历史悠久、内涵博大精深、传统优良的文化。它是中华民族几千年文明的结晶，除了儒家文化这个核心内容外，还包含有其他文化形态，如道家文化、佛教文化等等。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The Chinese traditional culture is the national culture of one reflection nationality special characteristics and style that the Chinese civilization evolves to collect, is in the national history the overall attribute of various ideological culture and ideology, refers to living, inherited development, has bright national characteristics, time-honored, connotation to be broad and profound for the Chinese nation who the Chinese nation and ancestor in Chinese region created for generations, traditional fine culture. It is a Chinese nation several thousand years of civilized crystallization, besides Confucianist culture essential content, but also contains to have other cultural shapes, such as Taoism culture, Buddhism culture and so on.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">2</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　中华传统文化是指中国历史上以个体农业经济为基础，以宗法家庭为背景，以儒家伦理道德为核心的社会文化体系。她是我们的祖先传承下来的丰厚遗产，曾长期处于世界领先的地位。她所蕴含的思维方式、价值观念、行为准则，一方面具有强烈的历史性、遗传性；另一方面又具有鲜活的现实性、变异性。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The Chinese traditional culture is to refer to the history of China is based on the individual farming economy, takes the clanlaw family as the background, social culture system centered on Confucian ethic morals. She is the rich heritage that our ancestors carry on, once was at the world leading position for a long time. Thinking mode, value concept and standard of conduct that she contains, on the one hand has the intense historicity and heredity; On the other hand also has the bright feasibility and changeability.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">3</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　中华民族在创造灿烂中华文明的过程中，经过五千多年的锤炼和洗礼，形成了具有强大生命力的传统文化。学者顾冠华认为“中国几千年文明发展史在特定的自然环境、经济形式、政治结构、意识形态的作用下形成、积累和流传下来，并且至今仍在影响当代文化的‘活’的中国古代文化。它既以有关的物化的经典文献、文化物品等客体形式存在和延续，又广泛地以民族的思维方式、价值观念、伦理道德、性格特征、审美趣味、知识结构、行为规范、风尚习俗等主体形式存在和延续。”而优秀的传统文化则是中华民族五千年文化积淀的精华，蕴含着推进中国社会发展的哲学思想、科学精神和人文精神，也为每一位中华儿女的成长提供了丰富的精神资源和文化背景。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The Chinese nation in the process of creation bright Chinese civilization, after more than 5000 years of temperance and baptism, formed had the traditional culture of vigorous vitality. Scholar Gu Guanhua thinks that "Chinese several thousand years of civilization development history ideology forms, accumulate and spread in the specific the function of natural environment, the economic form, the political structure and, and still in influence present age culture 'living 'ancient China culture. It not only exists and continues by related transformation classical document, cultural goods and other object forms, and widely exists and continues by nationality the thinking mode, value concept, moral principle, characteristics feature, aesthetic interest, knowledge structure, behavior standards, prevailing custom and other main forms." But the outstanding traditional culture is the essence that the Chinese nation in 5000 the culture will accumulate, will contain is advancing the philosophic thinking, the spirit of science and the humane spirit Chinese social development, has provided the rich spiritual resource and cultural background for the growth of each China's youth.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">4</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　李瑞环同志深刻指出：“中华民族传统文化源远流长，博大精深，对中华民族的形成、繁衍、统一及其自立于世界民族之林，起到了不可估量的作用，对人类文明的进步和发展，也产生了极其深远的影响。作为华夏子孙，我们有责任把祖先留下的这一极其丰厚、极其宝贵的文化遗产保护好、整理好、继承好，并在此基础上有所创造、有所前进。” 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Comrade Li Ruihuan profoundly pointed out: "Traditional Chinese culture is well-established, broad and profound, multiplies, unifies and supports oneself to Chinese nation's formation in forest of the nation, played the inestimable role, to the progress and development of human civilization, has had the extremely profound influence. As the Huaxia descendants, we have responsibility to be extremely rich, extremely precious culture heritage protection that the ancestor stays behind, to reorganize, to inherit, and has created based on this, has gone forward."

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">5</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

一、传统文化的内涵、特点及其两重性

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

I. The connotation, characteristics and duality traditional culture

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">6</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（一）传统文化的内涵及其特点

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(A) The connotation and characteristics of traditional culture

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">7</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

1.传统文化的内涵

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

1. The connotation of traditional culture

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">8</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　传统文化作为一个大概念，是由传统、文化两个小概念组合而成的。所谓“传统”，从文化学角度诠释，是指世代传承的具有自身特点的社会历史因素，如逐代延续的思想道德、风俗习惯、文学艺术、制度规范等。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The traditional culture as a major concept, is combined by the traditions and cultural two minor concepts. So-called "tradition", from the cultural science angle annotation, refers to the generation inheritance has own characteristics social history factor, such as by concept, manners and customs, literary arts, institution generation extension.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">9</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　“文化”一词，在中国古代本指“文治教化”，与武力征服相对举。《周易• 贲卦》（《彖传》）说：“观乎人文，以化成天下。"可以被看做是文化的原始提法。然而我们今天使用的“文化”一词，其含义与古代不尽一致，它是19世纪末期通过日文转译从西方引进的。1871年，英国学者泰勒在他发表的《原始文化》一书中给文化下了一个著名的定义：“所谓文化，乃是包括知识、信仰、艺术、道德，法律、习俗以及包括作为社会成员的个人而获得的其他任何能力、习惯在内的一个综合体。”

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The word "culture", refers to "civilizing role of government enlightenment" in Chinese Deboin, lifts with military conquest relatively. "Book of Change Ben Gua" ("Commentary on the diagrams of the yi jing") said: "View humanities, to turn into the world. "Can be regarded as the primitive formulation of culture. However today we use the word "culture", its meaning was inconsistent with the ancient times, it was introduced from the West through Japanese translation in the late 19th century. In 1871, British scholar Taylor to the culture has given a famous definition in "Primitive Culture" that he published: "So-called culture, is including knowledge, belief, art and morals, the legal, custom as well as including any other ability and a custom of complex compound taking individual of members of different social classes obtaining."

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">10</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　中国的学者一般都采用《辞海》对文化的界定：

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The scholars in China use "Dictionary" generally to the limits of culture:

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">11</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　“从广义上来说，指人类社会历史实践过程中所创造的物质财富的总和。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　“Broadly, refers to the sum total of material wealth in the human society historical practice process creating.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">12</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　　从狭义来说，指社会的意识形态，以及与之相适应的制度和组织机构。” 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　　From the narrow sense, refers to the ideology of society, as well as to the system and that the organizations and agencies it adapts. ”

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">13</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　需要指出的是文化作为一种观念形态的东西，总是处于流变与整合过程中。因此，并不是所有历史上出现过的文化都可称之为传统文化。而只有那些具有重要价值、具有生命活力的文化才得以积淀、保存、延续下来，成为后世文化的主要组成部分。我们将这些具有重要价值、具有生命活力因而得以积淀、保存、延续下来的文化称之为传统文化。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　What needs to point out is the culture as a thing of ideology, is always in changing and conformity process. Therefore, is not all historically has presented the culture may call the traditional culture. Only then these have the important value, to have the life vigor culture to accumulate, preserve and continue, becomes the key component of later generation culture. We have the important value, to have the culture that the life vigor can therefore accumulate, preserve and continue to call the traditional culture these.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">14</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　中华传统文化，即中华民族的传统文化，就是指根植于中华大地肥沃土壤之中，在长期的历史发展过程中形成和发展起来，保留在中华民族之间具有稳定形态的，世代传承并影响整个社会历史的，宏大的古典文化体系。除儒家、道家、法家和佛教学说之外，还包括历史、文物、书法、服饰、陵墓、医学、农学、天文、地理等古籍文书。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The Chinese traditional culture, namely the traditional culture of Chinese nation, refers to being rooted in the China rich soil, forms and develops in the long-term historical development process, retains has the stable shape among the Chinese nation, the generation inheritance and affects the entire social history, great classical culture system. Besides Confucianist, Taoism, legalist school and Buddhism theory, but also includes the history, cultural relic, calligraphy, clothing, mausoleum, medicine, agronomy, astronomy, geography and other old book copy clerks.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">15</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　传统文化是历史的结晶，但它并只是博物馆里的陈列品，而是有着鲜活生命的东西。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The traditional culture is the crystallization of history, but it and is only the exhibit in museum, but has the colorful life thing.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">16</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

2．传统文化的特点

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

2. The characteristics of traditional culture

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">17</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　中国传统文化有各种表现形态，居中心地位的是以伦理道德为核心，以儒家伦理中心主义为出发点的信念。中国传统伦理政治思想，不仅决定了中国古代人的文化人格，而且决定中国传统文化的民族特征。除了伦理政治型文化这一总的特征之外，中国传统文化还具有以下特点：

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The Chinese traditional culture has various performance shapes, those who are the central position is centered on the moral principle, takes the Confucian ethic center principle as the starting point faith. Chinese traditional ethics political thinking, not only has decided the cultural personality of Chinese ancient people, but also decides the Chinese traditional culture the national characters. Besides ethics politics culture total characteristics, the Chinese traditional culture also has the following characteristics:

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">18</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（1）同一性与多样性的统一: 中国传统文化绵延不绝，形成了世界上极具生命力的文化传统。在人类6000年的文明史上，只有中国文化按照自己的轨道不问断地运行一直到今天。而其他国家大多出现过断层，有的甚至走向消亡。中国文化历经艰辛，在数千年的发展中经历了多民族、各地域文化的融合发展，以汉民族文化为主体、以中原文化为核心的中国传统文化，逐渐融合其他少数民族文化和周围地域文化、形成了同一性与多样性相结合的发展态势。已深深地融进全体华人的思想意识和行为规范之中，渗透到社会政治、经济，特别是精神生活的各个领域，成为影响社会历史发展，支配人们思想行为和日常生活的强大力量。它对于民族的生存与延续发挥着不可估量的深远影响，它有着顽强的生命力，同时对于外来文化有着宽厚的包容性和强大的同化力。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(1) Identity and multiple unification: The Chinese traditional culture be continuous unceasingly, formed in the world to have the cultural tradition of vitality. In humanity in 6000 history of civilization, only then the Chinese culture does not ask the operation according to own track to today. But other countries mostly have presented fault, some even move toward withering away. The Chinese culture has been through repeatedly difficultly, experienced the fusion development of various multi-ethnic and realm cultures in several thousand years of development, takes the Han nationality culture as the main body and Chinese traditional culture centered on area south of Yellow River culture, gradually fuses other national minority culture and surrounding realm culture, has formed the development momentum that the identity and multiplicity unified. Deeply melted in all Chinese's ideology and behavior standards, seeps to the social politics and economy, each domain of especially spiritual life, becomes the influence social historical development, controls the people thinking and behavior and daily life great power. It and continues regarding the survival of nationality is displaying the inestimable far-reaching significance, it has the tenacious vitality, simultaneously has the generous tolerance and formidable assimilatory power regarding the external culture.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">19</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（2）民族性与世界性的统一: 传统文化具有鲜明的中华民族的显著特点和特征，渗透着古老东方民族的聪明和智慧。世界上各个国家各个民族都有自己的传统文化，虽然说是传统但它并不是一成不变的，是随着各个国家民族在相互的交往活动中，相互学习、相互吸收而不断充实发展自己。这种发展，是相互融合，使自己更加完美、更具有自己国家民族的特色。随着漫长的历史交往，各个国家民族的文化日益发展成“合而不同”的融合，逐步成为多元统一体的全球文化。正如一位大学者说的，越是民族性的东西越具有世界性，越具有全球性。失掉了民族性的东西，就说不上什么世界性、全球性。因为世界本身就是一个多元化的统一体，离开多元化、统一体也就没有存在的价值了。我国的传统文化在发生、发展和演变的过程中，以博大的胸怀、开阔的视野，融合了我国各民族文化、外来文化的优点和长处，逐步丰富完善了自我。随着世界文化的交融，必然很自然地走向全球化。如儒家孔子的“天下观”，道家老子、庄子的“自然观"精神已在世界学术界广为传播。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(2) National characteristics and worldwide basis unification: The traditional culture has the outstanding feature and characteristics of bright Chinese nation, is seeping the intelligence and intelligence of ancient Oriental nation. Each country in the world each nationality has own traditional culture, although said that is traditional it is not but irrevocable, along with each nationality in the mutual exchange activities, the mutual study, absorbs mutually, but continually enriches develops itself. This development, fuses mutually, making oneself more perfect, has the characteristics of oneself nationality. Along with long historical contact, the culture day all the more generating of each nationality "about, but is different" the fusion, gradually becomes the global culture of multi-dimensional entity. Just like a scholar said that more is national characteristics thing Vietnam has the worldwide basis, Vietnam has the global character. Lost the national characteristics thing, cannot say any worldwide basis and global character. Because the world is in itself a multiplex entity, leaves value that the multiplication and entity have not had. The traditional culture of our country, the process of development and in evolution, by the great mind and open field of vision, fused the merit and strong point of various our country national culture and external culture, gradually richly has improved. Along with blending of world culture, inevitably very natural moves toward the globalization. If Confucianist Confucius "world view", Taoism Laozi, Zhuangzi "view " spirit has disseminated in the world academic community widely.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">20</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（3）继承性与创新性的统一: 中国传统文化强调前代文化遗产的价值，充分宣扬传统本身得以存在和流传的合理性，虽然它也有起伏跌宕，并多次面临挑战，但一次又一次表现出巨大的再生能力。它在一个漫长而曲折的形成过程中，经历了无数个后人继承前人又发展前人，虚心学习前人又丰富前人，依据时代需求又超越前人，这样一个周而复始、连续不断的接力运动，付出了几十代人坚持不懈地刻苦努力和巨大心血，才逐步形成、不断补充、不断完善成熟起来的，来之不易。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(3) Succession and innovative unification: The Chinese traditional culture emphasized before, the value of generation of cultural heritages, publicizes the rationality that the tradition itself can have and spread fully, although it also ups and downs, and faces the challenge repeatedly, but shows the huge reproductive property time and time again. It in a long and winding forming process, experienced countless posterity to inherit the predecessor to develop the predecessor, studied the predecessor to enrich the predecessor modestly, surpassed the predecessor according to the time demand, this kind and relay movement continuously again and again, has paid dozens generations of relentlessly assiduous diligently and huge painstaking care, gradually formed, supplement and continually to improve be mature unceasingly, hard-won.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">21</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（二）传统文化的两重性

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(B) The duality of traditional culture

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">22</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　五千年的文明史，中华民族创造了著称于世的文化。其中儒家文化的发展及演变是贯穿于中国古代文化的主线。就内容上说，儒家的仁政王道，道家的清静无为、以退为守，法家的循名责实、信赏必罚，这三者构成中国古代文化的三位一体基本要素，浸透于民族的性格和心理中。其基本价值系统是以儒家体系为主干，同时又兼容道、法、墨等诸子百家之长。但它并不是珠玑而是混有沙石。因此，对这份遗产既不能完全抛弃，又不能全盘搬用，必须去其糟粕，取其精华，批判继承，推陈出新，创造中国社会主义现代化新文化。毛泽东同志指出：“中国的长期封建社会中，创造了灿烂的古代文化。清理古代文化的发展过程，剔除其封建性的糟粕，吸收其民主性的精华，是发展民族新文化提高民族自信心的必要条件；但是绝不能无批判地兼收并蓄。必须将古代封建统治阶级的一切腐朽的东西和古代优秀的人民文化即多少带有民主性和革命性的东西区别开来。⋯ ⋯ 我们必须尊重自己的历史，决不能割断历史。但是这种尊重，是给历史一定的科学地位，是尊重历史辨证法的发展，而不是颂古非今，不是赞扬任何封建的毒素。毛泽东同志的这段话，清楚地告诉人们对中国传统文化应取的态度,但同样有他所处特定时代背景。取精用弘，批判地加以继承。那么，怎样进行批判地继承呢? 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　5000 history of civilization, the Chinese nation have created the culture of being celebrated worldwide. And the development and evolution of Confucianist culture passed through in the master line of ancient China culture. Said on the content in that the policy of benevolence kingly way of Confucianist, the quietism and inaction of Taoism, takes drawing back as to defend, forcing facts to fit name and rewards and punishments carried out rigorously and impartially of legalist school, the three constituted the Trinity base element of ancient China culture, soaked in the disposition and psychology of nationality. The core value system takes the Confucianist system as the branch, simultaneously and compatible road, France and Mexico and other long of all of various schools of thought. But it is not the pearl, but mixes the grit. Therefore, to this inheritance not only cannot get rid completely, cannot overall apply mechanically, must go to its dregs, takes its essence, the critique inherits, weeds through the old to bring forth the new, creates the socialism in China modernization new culture. Comrade Mao Zedong pointed out: "In the long-term feudal society of China, has created the bright ancient civilization. The developing process of cleaning up ancient civilization, rejected its feudalistic dregs, absorbed its democratic essence, was develops the national new culture to enhance the national self-confidence the essential condition; However must have the critique to swallow anything and everything uncritically. Must many have democratic and revolutionary thing all decayed things and ancient outstanding people cultures of ancient feudal rule social class distinguishes. ⋯⋯ we must respect our history, cannot cut off the history. However this respect, to historical certain scientific status, respects the development of historical diagnostic method, but does not praise Gu Feijin, toxin that does not praise any feudalism. Comrade Mao Zedong's these words, told the people clearly to the manner that the Chinese traditional culture should take, but had his specific background similarly. Selects the essence, the critique inherits. Then, how to carry on the critique to inherit?

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">23</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　其精华部分主要有：

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The excellent part mainly has:

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">24</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（1）刚健有为，自强不息： 刚健有为、自强不息的进取精神一直居中国文化传统的主导地位。《易传》日：“天行健，君子以自强不息”，“地势坤，君子以厚德载物。”其意是说“天”的德性是健运不己，人们应该仿效它，刚健有为，奋发进取；“地"的德性是顺育万物、包孕万物、哺育万物，人们也应该仿效它，兼容并包，广收博采。孔子提倡“发愤忘食、乐以忘忧”的人生追求，孟子崇尚“富贵不能淫、贫贱不能移、威武不能屈”的“大丈夫”气概。屈原在《渔父》中愤然写道：“举世皆浊吾独清，举世皆醉吾独醒。”正是在这种精神鼓舞下，中国人对真理孜孜以求，对外敌侵略拼死抵抗，铸造出知难而进、吃苦耐劳、自力更生的民族性格。进取的人生态度，在成才的道路上努力奋斗，自强不息。这些都集中表现了中华民族积极进取、永不停息的坚强意志和非凡气度。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(1) Vigor promising, strives constantly for self-improvement: Enterprising spirit that the vigor promising, strives constantly for self-improvement has been the Chinese culture traditional dominant position. "Easy Biography" date: "Day line is healthy, the gentleman to strive constantly for self-improvement", "topography Kun, the gentleman carries the thing by thick Germany."The meaning was to say "day" the morality moral character transports non-oneself healthily, the people should imitate it, vigorous promising, forged ahead; "" The morality moral character is pregnant along Yu Wanwu, packages the myriad things and nurture myriad things, the people should also imitate it, includes all kinds together, receives Bo Cai broadly. Confucius advocated that "forgets to eat and to forget sad happily" the life pursuit, Mencius advocates "riches and honor cannot obscene and lowly unable to move and not can be subdued by force" "real man" spirit. Qu Yuan wrote in "Old fisherman" angrily: "The whole world is all muddy I to be alone, the whole world is all drunk I to awake alone."Under this spiritual inspiration, the Chinese diligently strives after to the truth, invades to the foreign enemy resists at risk of life, the casting leaves the national character of advancing in spite of difficulties, bearing hardships and standing hard work and relies on one's own effort to revive. Enterprising attitude towards life, struggles on the path of maturing diligently, strives constantly for self-improvement. These mainly display the stubborn will and extraordinary bearing that the Chinese nation will have ceased positively enterprisingly and never.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">25</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（2）天人合一，以人为本：所谓天主要指广大的自然界，天人关系主要指人与自然的关系，天人合一思想认为，人是自然界的一部分，人是组成自然系统不可或缺的要素之一；自然界有普遍规律，人也应该服从这个规律；人类社会的道德原则与自然规律是一致的；人生的最高理想应该是天人之间的协调。“天人合一”的思想给予了我们许多启示。中国传统文化注重天人合一，但是，在天地人之间，以人为中心，即以人为本。如，孔子主张的“不语怪、力、乱、神”和“未能事人，焉能事鬼”这种思想影响巨大，他虽然不能否定鬼神的存在，但是对其采取存疑的态度，即存而不论；而将现实中的人放在第一位，关注人的生命。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(2) Harmony of nature and man, humanist: The so-called day mainly refers to the general nature, the beauty relates mainly refers to the human and natural relations, the harmony of nature and man thought believes that the human is part of nature, the human is one of the composition natural system indispensable essential factors; The nature has the universal law, human should also abide by this rule; The ethical principle of human society is consistent with the natural law; The most high ideal of life should be the coordination between beauties. "Harmony of nature and man" the thought has given us the enlightenment. The Chinese traditional culture pays great attention to the harmony of nature and man, but, among the world people, is centered on the human, namely humanist. Confucius position "did not speak strange, strength, chaotic, god" and "not the strong point person, strong point ghost" this ideological influence was huge, although he cannot deny existence of ghosts and gods, but had the manner of leaving undecided to it, namely left undecided; But places the first person in reality, the life of attention person.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">26</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（3）修养德性，人际协调：儒家文化是伦理文化，主张“道德至上”，强调以“仁让为贵，以孝悌为尚，以忠敬为美”的人生理想。在古代思想家们看来，天是道德之天，人是道德之人，甚至一草一木也得道而生，有德之品性。在这种道德辐射之下，主张“仁者爱人”、“以和为贵”，讲究“老吾老以及人之老，幼吾幼以及人之幼”的和谐人际关系。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(3) Training morality moral character, interpersonal coordination: The Confucianist culture is the ethics culture, advocated that "morals are supreme", stressed that takes "kernel to make for expensive, took the filial piety as still, took the loyal respect as US" ideal of life. Looked like in the ancient thinkers, day was the day of morals, the human was the person of morals, even every bit of property also obtained enlightenment to live, had the moral character of Germany. Under this moral radiation, advocated that "savant spouse" and "peacing is precious", is fastidious "is old I old as well as old of person, young I young as well as young of person" harmony interpersonal relationship.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">27</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

（4）集体本位，天下为公：西方文化崇尚的是个体本位，而中国传统文化以家庭为中心，以集体为本位，讲究“贵群”。在个体、局部与集体、整体发生冲突时，主张牺牲前者而保护后者，这就是所说的“天下为公”。天下兴亡、匹夫有责，爱国是每个人义不容辞的责任。于是有了范仲淹的“先天下之忧而忧，后天下之乐而乐。”文天祥在生命的最后一刻仍然高吟：“人生自古谁无死，留取丹心照汗青。”

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

(4) Collective standard, world belong to all: What the Western culture advocates is individual standard, but the Chinese traditional culture is centered on the family, takes the collective as the standard, is fastidious about "expensive crowd". When the individual, partial and collective and whole has the conflict, advocated that sacrificed the former to protect the latter, this is "world belong to all that" said. The world rise and fall and everyone has a share of responsibility, patriotic are each person unshirkable responsibility. Therefore had Fan Zhongyan "is concerned first about the welfare of all, enjoys the fruits after the people do."Wen Tianxiang in life at the last minute still Gao Yin: "Life who not died since old times, remains to take the loyalty according to the bamboo writing slips."

</td></tr>
