　　总之，对待中国传统文化必须注意辨证地分析，批判地继承。然而批判的继承最终目的是为了发展和创新。这就是说在批判地继承中国传统文化的基础上，吸收有价值的外来文化，不断丰富和发展中华传统文化。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　In brief, treats the Chinese traditional culture to pay attention dialectical to analyze, the critique inherits. However the inheritance ultimate goal of critique is to develop and innovate. That is in the critique builds on the Chinese traditional culture in the foundation, absorbs the valuable external culture, enriches and develops the Chinese traditional culture unceasingly.

